                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-energy-consumption synthetic ammonia production device",
                    "一种低能耗合成氨生产装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a low-energy-consumption synthetic ammonia production device which comprises a synthetic ammonia reactor, a feed port of the synthetic ammonia reactor is communicated with a raw material gas mixing tank, a discharge port of the synthetic ammonia reactor is connected with an inlet of a membrane separator, a gas inlet of the synthetic ammonia reactor is connected with a raw material nitrogen input pipe through a nitrogen branch, and a gas outlet of the synthetic ammonia reactor is communicated with a gas-liquid separator after passing through a cooling assembly; the raw material gas mixing tank is respectively connected with a raw material nitrogen input pipe and a raw material hydrogen input pipe through a nitrogen main path and a hydrogen pipeline; a permeation side outlet of the membrane separator is connected with a gas outlet of the synthetic ammonia reactor, and a retentate side outlet of the membrane separator is connected with a feed port of the synthetic ammonia reactor after passing through a circulating gas mixing tank; a liquid ammonia outlet of the gas-liquid separator is communicated with the liquid ammonia collector, and a gas outlet of the gas-liquid separator is communicated with the circulating gas mixing tank. The liquid ammonia separation temperature can be greatly increased, a liquid ammonia cooling system does not need to be additionally arranged, energy consumption is effectively reduced, and energy conservation and environmental protection are facilitated."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种低能耗合成氨生产装置，包括合成氨反应器，其进料口与原料气混合罐后相连通，其出料口与膜分离器的进口相连，其进气口通过氮气支路与原料氮气输入管相连，其出气口经过冷却组件后与气液分离器相连通；所述原料气混合罐分别通过氮气主路和氢气管路与原料氮气输入管和原料氢气输入管相连；所述膜分离器的渗透侧出口与所述合成氨反应器的出气口相连，其渗余侧出口与经过循环气混合罐后与所述合成氨反应器的进料口相连；所述气液分离器的液氨出口与液氨收集器相连通，其气体出口与所述循环气混合罐相连通。本发明可使液氨的分离温度得到极大的提高，不再需要额外设置液氨冷却系统，有效降低了能耗，利于节能环保。"
                }
